{"tid":910831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"D&G 創辦人涉稱「中國是屎國」　李冰冰、廸麗熱巴等內地明星杯葛時裝騷","createTime":"2018-11-21T12:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T12:51:59.000Z","uid":1174,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fafb939492bf4d52375d65c316686d6dd670768c","tid":910831,"uid":1174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:37:36.000Z","msg":"國際知名時裝品牌 D&amp;G （Dolce &amp; Gabbana）原訂今晚在上海舉行大型時裝展 The Great Show，不過品牌創辦人之一的 Stefano Gabbana 早前懷疑在 Instagram（IG） 與網民就品牌三條被指辱華短片內容激辯時，說出「中國就是屎國」，結果引起軒然大波。<br />\n章子怡、黃曉明、李冰冰、廸麗熱巴等多位獲邀出席 D&amp;G 時裝展的內地明星，今日紛紛在微博打出「祖國高於一切」、「我愛我的祖國」等口號，表明拒絕出席 D&amp;G 活動。Stefano Gabbana 及 D&amp;G 今午均在 IG 發聲明指戶口被黑客入侵，已尋求法律協助，而 Stefano Gabbana 更在 IG 寫上「I love China and the Chinese Culture」。<br />\n事件成為今天內地最熱話題，在微博熱搜榜首 10 位中，和事件有關的搜尋佔了 7 位，合共搜尋量達 1400 多萬次。事件起因，是 D&amp;G 在上周六開始，先後上載 3 條為宣傳 The Great Show 而拍的短片，片中一名細眼方面的中國女模特兒，先後用筷子吃大碗意大利粉、意式薄餅（Pizza）及 意式香炸甜卷（Cannolo），姿態顯得有點笨拙，例如把筷子當成刀叉，企圖切開薄餅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/D+G+創辦人涉稱「中國是屎國」辱華%E3%80%80章子怡等內地明星杯葛時裝騷-WnjpPg/?utm_source=oa&amp;utm_medium=all&amp;utm_campaign=1811210616&amp;utm_term=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Fpc%2Farticle%2FD%2BG%2B%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%98%AF%E5%B1%8E%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%8D%E8%BE%B1%E8%8F%AF%25E3%2580%2580%E7%AB%A0%E5%AD%90%E6%80%A1%E7%AD%89%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%8E%E6%98%9F%E6%9D%AF%E8%91%9B%E6%99%82%E8%A3%9D%E9%A8%B7-WnjpPg%2F%3Futm_source%3Doa%26utm_medium%3Dall%26utm_campaign%3D1811210616%26utm_term%3D2&d=sg4kdzOBGnbgirfSeSyDwy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=e0a6d821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/D+G+創辦人涉稱「中國是屎國」辱華%E3%80%80章子怡等內地明星杯葛時裝騷-WnjpPg/?utm_source=oa&amp;utm_medium=all&amp;utm_campaign=1811210616&amp;utm_term=2</a>"},{"pid":"7208b1b9a3990120a1c5ebf7a97a8a570d80791e","tid":910831,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"瑞典效應！"},{"pid":"66d2cb0d1950362ee86c55a88f84f122440619e9","tid":910831,"uid":16414,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"D&amp;G 都係香港本土運動發起人"},{"pid":"d3a3ec6a8b407fe859880df24674faf3fa132e8e","tid":910831,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66d2cb0d1950362ee86c55a88f84f122440619e9","tid":910831,"uid":16414,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"D&amp;G 都係香港本土運動發起人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"得罪群眾"},{"pid":"ce30ad915e797b4cb3ec9e39b91967be648fe91c","tid":910831,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:47:32.000Z","msg":"btw 我有時都用筷子食意粉喎"},{"pid":"9e3299da8e6f3f328e42c7daf92ddb43031667db","tid":910831,"uid":1174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42eaea31f11ad3560e0cf7fe80ed5e2665f49d1c","tid":910831,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">快點道歉！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}